<h2 style="margin:0 0 8px; color:#2E2E38; font-size:22px;">Sol Kòmanse!</h2>
<p style="margin:0 0 16px; color:#5D6345; font-size:14px;"><strong><%= @circle.name %></strong> gen tout manm li yo. Wonn 1 lanse kounye a!</p>

<div style="background:#fff; border:1px solid #d9d6c4; border-radius:14px; padding:14px 16px; margin-bottom:14px;">
  <div style="font-size:11px; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:1px; color:#5D6345; font-weight:700; margin-bottom:8px;">Enfòmasyon Sol</div>
  <div style="font-size:13px; color:#2E2E38;"><strong>Kontribisyon:</strong> <%= number_to_currency(@circle.amount, unit: @circle.htg? ? "HTG " : "USDC ") %> pa wonn</div>
  <div style="font-size:13px; color:#2E2E38;"><strong>Manm:</strong> <%= @circle.sol_memberships.count %></div>
  <div style="font-size:13px; color:#2E2E38;"><strong>Total Kès:</strong> <%= number_to_currency(@circle.payout_amount, unit: @circle.htg? ? "HTG " : "USDC ") %> pa wonn</div>
  <div style="font-size:13px; color:#2E2E38;"><strong>Kòmansman:</strong> <%= @circle.start_date&.strftime("%d %b %Y") %></div>
  <div style="font-size:13px; color:#2E2E38;"><strong>Fen:</strong> <%= @circle.end_date&.strftime("%d %b %Y") %></div>
</div>

<div style="background:#f0fdf4; border:1px solid #bbf7d0; border-radius:14px; padding:14px 16px; margin-bottom:14px;">
  <div style="font-size:13px; color:#166534; font-weight:700;">Ou gen 48 èdtan pou peye chak wonn. Peye a lè pou ogmante nivo kredi ou!</div>
</div>

<p style="margin:0;">
  <a href="<%= sol_circle_url(@circle.token) %>" style="color:#2E2E38; background:#C5A059; text-decoration:none; padding:10px 16px; border-radius:10px; font-weight:700; display:inline-block;">Wè Sol La</a>
</p>

<p style="margin:16px 0 0; color:#5D6345; font-size:13px;">Avèk respè,<br><strong>Priotelus</strong></p>
